---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import aboutImage from "../assets/about-us.png";
---

<section
	class="bg-white py-12 md:py-20 px-0 md:px-20 lg:pl-[calc((100%-1200px)/2+4rem)] xl:pl-[calc((100%-1600px)/2+5rem)] xl:pr-[calc((100%-1600px)/2+5rem)]"
>
	<div class="w-full max-w-[1600px] mx-auto group">
		<h2
			class="text-[32px] md:text-[40px] font-[300] text-black mb-10 tracking-tight px-6 md:px-0"
		>
			About Us
		</h2>

		<div
			class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row rounded-none md:rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-none md:shadow-xl min-h-[500px]"
		>
			<div class="lg:w-1/2 relative min-h-[350px] lg:min-h-full">
				<Image
					src={aboutImage}
					alt="Doctor with a mother and child"
					class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
				/>
			</div>

			<div
				class="lg:w-1/2 bg-primary p-10 md:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center"
			>
				<h3
					class="text-white text-[28px] md:text-[36px] font-[300] leading-tight mb-8"
				>
					Your Dedicated Partner for World-Class Healing in India.
				</h3>
				<p
					class="text-white/90 text-[15px] md:text-[16px] leading-[1.8] font-[300] tracking-wide"
				>
					MediTailor is a gateway for international patients to gain
					access to India's crème de la crème in healthcare services.
					Our mission is simple: high-precision healthcare,
					accessible, and affordable. We don't just provide healthcare
					services, we "tailor" your entire healthcare experience.
					From connecting you with a super-specialist surgeon to your
					medical visa, recovery stay, and everything in between, we
					are with you every step of the way. Your healthcare journey
					is unique, and so is ours – let's take this journey together
					with care, clarity, and quality
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
